description.undefined: The Catena-X Contact Ontology describes Business Partners.

definition.value: An address where a person works or an organisations is located.
A place is a specific location.
A organization is a group of people who work together to achieve a common goal.
An address that is a unique identifier for a specific location of a building.
An address where a person lives.
A product is a good or service that is offered for sale.
A person is a human being.
A string that identifies either a unique object or a unique class of objects.
